items.name: CURRENT
desc: a navigation bar is provided and navigation will be performed on the current/active form.
pressing the TAB key from the last control moves the focus to the first control in the tab order of the same record.
This is the default and most often encountered mode.

items.name: PAGE
desc: pressing the TAB key from the last control of a form moves the focus to the first control of the next form in the tab order.

items.name: RECORDS
desc: pressing the TAB key from the last control moves the focus to the first control in the tab order of the next record.
